    "name": "鼠鼠登月 Rocket Rats",
    "steam_appid": 3069810,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069810/extras/cdb0aafc641de012fe65eaa2cdffc659.poster.avif?t=1769349801\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069810/extras/cdb0aafc641de012fe65eaa2cdffc659.webm?t=1769349801\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069810/extras/cdb0aafc641de012fe65eaa2cdffc659.mp4?t=1769349801\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有系统就绪，准备升空！《鼠鼠登月》是一款类幸存者游戏，你将在月球上迎战一波又一波由奶酪组成的怪物。你扮演众多老鼠中的一员，负责为太空基地开采奶酪——方式很简单，用枪把它们轰飞就对了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069810/extras/e273455c53de09e28867ad8c46cd220c.poster.avif?t=1769349801\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069810/extras/e273455c53de09e28867ad8c46cd220c.webm?t=1769349801\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069810/extras/e273455c53de09e28867ad8c46cd220c.mp4?t=1769349801\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >月球上到处都是一心想攻击你的敌人。既然他们是奶酪做的，那正是求之不得！各类奶酪敌人会在不同波次中登场，迎战敌潮的时候务必小心，千万别被越来越多的敌人包围！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069810/extras/64adc9eccfb89363d751c8d84971c9ed.poster.avif?t=1769349801\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069810/extras/64adc9eccfb89363d751c8d84971c9ed.webm?t=1769349801\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069810/extras/64adc9eccfb89363d751c8d84971c9ed.mp4?t=1769349801\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了对抗不断壮大的敌潮，你可以在每一局游戏中获得各种不同的升级。从与你并肩作战、自动射击的星际盟友，到召唤闪电、施加毒素等减益效果，你始终能依照自己的游玩风格，选择最合适的强化方向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069810/extras/ced188e94b57321d54b57d0cce3a8986.poster.avif?t=1769349801\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069810/extras/ced188e94b57321d54b57d0cce3a8986.webm?t=1769349801\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069810/extras/ced188e94b57321d54b57d0cce3a8986.mp4?t=1769349801\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游玩次数越多，你能收集到的奶酪也越多。使用这些奶酪，你可以购买永久升级，并通过技能树系统提升角色能力，进一步强化你的构筑。解锁并游玩不同角色，例如战术家老鼠、身经百战的士兵、耒毛等等，每位角色都能带来截然不同的游戏体验。</p>",
